OL,3,CMerseyrail launches 'A Pound for Zoe's
OL,4,CPlace'
OL,6,FPassengers on the Merseyrail network
OL,7,Fare being prompted to donate "A Pound
OL,8,Ffor Zoe's Place" when buying tickets
OL,9,Fin the latest push to save a vital
OL,10,Fchildren's hospice.
OL,12,FZoe's Place has been in operation for
OL,13,Fthe last 30 years and had hoped to
OL,14,Fbuild a new #3.5m hospice close to its
OL,15,Fcurrent location in Yew Tree Lane,
OL,16,FLiverpool.
