OL,3,CMerseyrail launches 'A Pound for Zoe's
OL,4,CPlace'
OL,6,FBut, on 7 October trustees at the West
OL,7,FDerby hospice announced a lengthy
OL,8,Fplanning process left them no choice
OL,9,Fbut to close the hospice at the end of
OL,10,F2024 unless #5 million could be raised
OL,11,Fby 9 November.
OL,13,FSince the announcement, #2.5 million
OL,14,Fhas been donated and raised through
OL,15,Ffundraisers including a celebrity
OL,16,Fcomedy show and marathon livestreams.
