OL,3,CMerseyrail launches 'A Pound for Zoe's
OL,4,CPlace'
OL,6,FAs the deadline to secure the
OL,7,Fremaining money approaches, Merseyrail
OL,8,Fhas begun inviting its roughly 90,000
OL,9,Fdaily customers to donate #1 to Zoe's
OL,10,FPlace during the ticket purchasing
OL,11,Fprocess.
OL,13,FMerseyrail Managing Director Neil
OL,14,FGrabham said: "When we heard about the
OL,15,Fchallenges facing Zoe's Place the
OL,16,Fwhole Merseyrail team were focused on
OL,17,Fhelping in any way we could.
OL,19,F"We know many of our customers will
OL,20,Falso be looking for a way to show
OL,21,Ftheir support.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
