OL,3,CMerseyrail launches 'A Pound for Zoe's
OL,4,CPlace'
OL,6,F"This hospice has been a lifeline for
OL,7,Fcountless families, and we want to
OL,8,Fmake it as easy as possible for our
OL,9,Fcustomers to contribute to saving this
OL,10,Fvital service."
OL,12,FLiverpool West Derby MP Ian Byrne has
OL,13,Falso been raising money for Zoe's
OL,14,FPlace, and recently called on the
OL,15,FChancellor Rachel Reeves to review the
OL,16,Fway hospices are funded to ensure
OL,17,Fseriously ill children do "not have to
OL,18,Frely on charity to get the support
OL,19,Fthey need".
