OL,3,CMerseyrail launches 'A Pound for Zoe's
OL,4,CPlace'
OL,6,F"We are all working hard to make this
OL,7,Fhappen for the incredible children,
OL,8,Ffamilies and staff of this very
OL,9,Fspecial place in our city. It's
OL,10,Fcertainly a huge ask to raise #5
OL,11,Fmillion in a matter of weeks, but if
OL,12,Fany city can do this, it's Liverpool."
